LineNo: 12770189,

The pain in my hand pulled me from my thoughts. A medic rushed over to tend to the cut.

LineNo: 12770291,

Player_Romus: Thank you for attending.
en


"Thank you for attending."

LineNo: 12770393,

Sal Ignacius: We have so much we can do together...
en


"We have so much we can do together. I can help you, as I helped your father."

LineNo: 12770495,

Sal Ignacius: As your Grand Vizier, I will do wh...
en


"As your Grand Vizier, I will do whatever I can to guide you through the darkness with the light of God."

LineNo: 12770597,

Sal Ignacius: There are many in Rizia that would...
en


"There are many in Rizia that would rejoice to see a man of faith ascend to such an important post."

LineNo: 12770707,

Sal Ignacius: Such believers can be... utilized...
en


"Such believers can be... utilized to aid the goals of the crown. I pray you will make the right choice."

LineNo: 12770809,

Angelica Sazon: Before my exile, I was one of the...
en


"Before my exile, I was one of the most educated noblewomen in Brenas. On Caleqabiz, I spent much of my time reading about the principles of governance."

LineNo: 12770911,

Angelica Sazon: Appoint me as Vizier and you can e...
en


"Appoint me as Vizier and you can expect both complete honesty and undying loyalty. Remember, I turned my own husband over to your father."

LineNo: 12771013,

Angelica Sazon: That is what I can offer to you an...
en


"That is what I can offer to you and to the crown. Nothing more, nothing less."

LineNo: 12771115,

Axel Reinhart: I ask you: What better action to s...
en


"I ask you: What better action to signify the friendship between Rizians and Palesians?"

LineNo: 12771217,

Axel Reinhart: This would be the logical choice,...
en


"This would be the logical choice, and I think you know it."

LineNo: 12771319,

Axel Reinhart: If you make me your Grand Vizier,...
en


"If you make me your Grand Vizier, I assure you that it will guarantee the trust of Palesians and along with it, the international community..."

LineNo: 12771421,

Axel Reinhart: I am also a capable politician and...
en


"I am also a capable politician and a ruthless negotiator, as you have experienced firsthand. I can provide you with contacts that nobody else can."

LineNo: 12771523,

Axel Reinhart: What better move to stir the heart...
en


"What better move to stir the hearts of your people? Romus, the Great Unifier! Your name will be written down in history."

LineNo: 12771625,

Axel Reinhart: That is my pitch, if you will, You...
en


"That is my pitch, if you will, Your Majesty."

LineNo: 12771727,

Rico Toras: You know very well what I am capab...
en


"You know very well what I am capable of, cousin."

LineNo: 12771829,

Rico Toras: I know how to wage war. I know how...
en


"I know how to wage war. I know how to maintain security. It sounds like I fill both of the roles required from this post."

LineNo: 12771931,

Rico Toras: You already know the great work I'...
en


"You already know the great work I've done as Chief of Police here in Porte Drazon. No need to delve further into that."

LineNo: 12772033,

Rico Toras: But that is not my only merit, as...
en


"But that is not my only merit, as you know. Let's say that the fruits of my extra-curricular activities are respected in the palace and the country."

LineNo: 12772135,

Rico Toras: My father may be good, but I assur...
en


"My father may be good, but I assure you, I am better."

LineNo: 12772237,

Rico Toras: As a Toras, I also think it is goo...
en


"As a Toras, I also think it is good to keep things in the family."

LineNo: 12772339,

Taddeus Azaro: All my life I have fought for this...
en


"All my life I have fought for this country. I bled for it. I went through hell for it."

LineNo: 12772441,

Taddeus Azaro: I know the ins and outs of our cou...
en


"I know the ins and outs of our country's military structure. More importantly, I command the respect of the Rizian Armed Forces and House Azaro."

LineNo: 12772543,

Taddeus Azaro: I know every single one of our Gen...
en


"I know every single one of our General Staff because I trained them. I fought alongside them."

LineNo: 12772645,

Taddeus Azaro: War will come to Rizia someday, si...
en


"War will come to Rizia someday, sire. And to protect the interests of my proud kingdom, I am ready to die a thousand deaths."

LineNo: 12772747,

Taddeus Azaro: My daughter is ready to step aside...
en


"My daughter is ready to step aside. She has another role to play now."

LineNo: 12772849,

Titus Gordion: I protected you and your father fo...
en


"I protected you and your father for many years as part of the Golden Guard and hopefully I will do so for many more."

LineNo: 12772951,

Titus Gordion: My entire life, I always felt that...
en


"My entire life, I always felt that in order to do my job better, I needed more and more of a say in matters."

LineNo: 12773053,

Titus Gordion: I want to be elevated to a positio...
en


"I want to be elevated to a position that will allow me to have that say."

LineNo: 12773155,

Titus Gordion: Trust in me and the Golden Guard,...
en


"Trust in me and the Golden Guard, and security will never be a worry in Rizia again."

LineNo: 12773257,

Titus Gordion: Thank you.
en


"Thank you."

LineNo: 12773359,

Daria de Rava: During my tenure at the House of D...
en


"During my tenure at the House of Delegates, I made many successful career moves and also ended others' careers."

LineNo: 12773461,

Daria de Rava: I have determined that this is the...
en


"I have determined that this is the best move for me."

LineNo: 12773563,

Daria de Rava: I and my family still have conside...
en


"I and my family still have considerable influence in international investment circles, and I have accumulated numerous contacts that might be of use to us."

LineNo: 12773665,

Daria de Rava: Treasurer of Rizia is a position t...
en


"Treasurer of Rizia is a position that requires more than mere number-crunching. One needs considerable political finesse."

LineNo: 12773767,

Russello Montoro: That's right. I want this job so m...
en


"That's right. I want this job so much I'm willing to go through *all* the formalities. I even bought a new tie."

LineNo: 12773869,

Russello Montoro: I've already helped make Rizia mon...
en


"I've already helped make Rizia money. Think about how much more I could do as treasurer."

LineNo: 12773971,

Russello Montoro: Just look at how much gold we're h...
en


"Just look at how much gold we're hauling out of the ground right now. All thanks to me."

LineNo: 12774073,

Russello Montoro: Not to mention that if you're look...
en


"Not to mention that if you're looking to get closer to ATO... well, I can help you with that. If you know what I mean."

LineNo: 12774175,

Russello Montoro: All apologies to the old gal Werne...
en


"All apologies to the old gal Werner, but this is the best deal you can get."

LineNo: 12774277,

Vina Toras: Father. I know you still see me as...
en


"Father. I know you still see me as your little girl. Maybe you don't think that I am ready."

LineNo: 12774379,

Vina Toras: But, I have been on your council f...
en


"But, I have been on your council for some time now. I understand its intricacies very well."

LineNo: 12774481,

Vina Toras: Laurento has been like a grandfath...
en


"Laurento has been like a grandfather to me, but he's past his prime and you know it. It's time for the younger generation to represent Rizia on the global stage."

LineNo: 12774583,

Vina Toras: As for me... well, you know better...
en


"As for me... well, you know better than anybody that work is all I have."

LineNo: 12774685,

Vina Toras: We have had our differences. But p...
en


"We have had our differences. But please. Grant me this."

LineNo: 12774787,

Narrator: The ritual had finally ended.
en


The ritual had finally ended.

LineNo: 12774889,

Narrator: I looked at the bright red, sizzlin...
en


I looked at the bright red, sizzling molten gold until my eyes began to water.

LineNo: 12775643,

Angelica Sazon: I do not only ask this of you as t...
en


"I do not only ask this of you as the mother of the Prince Consort."

LineNo: 12775745,

Angelica Sazon: By reinstating me as Duchess of Br...
en


"By reinstating me as Duchess of Brenas, you showed deep faith in my capabilities and in my noble house."

LineNo: 12775847,

Angelica Sazon: By bringing me back from exile, yo...
en


"By bringing me back from exile, you showed that House Toras was ready to place its faith in House Sazon once more."

LineNo: 12775949,

Angelica Sazon: I can think of no better way to re...
en


"I can think of no better way to return that gesture of faith than to serve on your council."

LineNo: 12776329,

Angelica Sazon: You already trusted my judgement o...
en


"You already trusted my judgement once, when you cancelled the ill-advised reforms you were planning."

LineNo: 12776709,

Angelica Sazon: I know you hunger for change. I ca...
en


"I know you hunger for change. I can help you achieve your goals while keeping the nobility satisfied."

LineNo: 12776811,

Angelica Sazon: And I am still prepared to keep th...
en


"And I am still prepared to keep the more... unruly elements of my house in line."

LineNo: 12777191,

Axel Reinhart: I realize that it's rather unortho...
en


"I realize that it's rather unorthodox to serve as the principal advisor to one's father-in-law. Rest assured that my own interests will come second to those of the Toras royal family. Every time."

LineNo: 12777293,

Axel Reinhart: I realize that it's rather unortho...
en


"I realize that it's rather unorthodox to serve as the principal advisor to a man nearly twice my age. Rest assured that my own interests will come second to yours. Every time."

LineNo: 12777673,

Player_Romus: I reject all of your petitions. Hu...
en


"I reject all of your petitions. Hugo Toras will remain my Grand Vizier."

LineNo: 12778059,

Rico Toras: Respectfully, after deposing me an...
en


"Respectfully, after deposing me and shooting my dog... this is the least you can do."

LineNo: 12778161,

Rico Toras: Respectfully, after deposing me as...
en


"Respectfully, after deposing me as Duke of Iza... this is the least you can do."

LineNo: 12778541,
